# Finger Sensitivity Plan

## Goal Description
Make the Ring finger easier to trigger (more sensitive) while keeping other fingers at the normal 0.10 threshold.

## User Review Required
None.

## Proposed Changes
### files
#### [MODIFY] [app.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/app.py)
- **Configuration**:
    - `VELOCITY_THRESHOLD_DEFAULT = 0.10`.
    - `VELOCITY_THRESHOLD_SENSITIVE = 0.05` (For Ring).
- **Logic**:
    - Inside loop:
        ```python
        threshold = VELOCITY_THRESHOLD_SENSITIVE if f_name == "Ring" else VELOCITY_THRESHOLD_DEFAULT
        if speed > threshold ...
        ```

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Run app.
- Tap Index finger lightly -> Should NOT trigger (needs > 0.1).
- Tap Ring finger lightly -> SHOULD trigger (needs > 0.05).
